@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_vronun(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (0.21 * 0.41)
    v0 = (((v0 + 0.62 + v2 + 0.03) + 0.43) / v2)
    v2 = (wp.exp(v1) - wp.sin(v2))
    v1 = 0.86
    v0 = wp.abs(v0)
    v0 = wp.cos(wp.sin((tmp + 0.43 / v1 + 0.76)))
    data[tid] = v0
